summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 5E, page 43, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in James Division, Green Lake Addition, east 60 ft. of south 1/2 of Block 10, Portion of Section 5-24-4, located on the northwest corner of East 65th St. and Brooklyn Ave. as Community Business (BC) Zone.
